---
title: Chicken with Dijon-Apricot Glaze plus Kale Slaw & Rice
description: Looking for the perfect finishing touch for tender pork filet? This quick savory-sweet glaze is made with apricot jam, Dijon mustard, and a swirl of butter for an irresistibly delicious balance of flavors. Serve the pork with a crisp slaw of kale, broccoli, and Brussels sprouts and a side of fluffy rice for a meal that’s destined for repeats.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66fc16a2846cedc69c6d7d0d-c9f42ca2.jpeg
